quran[69]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  29,2,"E yim…ďe …ďen cikku …ďe ngaccirte nii, fii …ďe wi'ii: ""Min ngooŇč…óinii!"" Hara …ďe pitninaaka?"
  29,3,"GooŇč…óii, Min pitninii …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe. Maa Alla fe√Ī√Īin, fii gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen, maa O fe√Ī√Īin kadi, fii fenoo…ďe …ďen."
  29,4,"Kaa gollu…ďe bon…ói …ďen cikku, won'nde …ďe laawoto Min? ko …ďe √Īaawata kon bonii!"
  29,5,"Kala taw…óo homo njortii kawroygol e Alla, ko pellet, lajal Alla ngal, ko hewtaygal. Ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ngandu…óo on."
  29,6,"Kala kadi tii…ónii…óo, ko hoore-makko o tii…ónanii, tawde pellet, Alla ko jon'dinii…óo e tageefo ngon."
  29,7,"∆Āeen non gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, ma Min momtan …ďe bon…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, Min njo…ďitra …ďe, ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko …ďe ngollatnoo kon."
  29,8,"Min njamirii ne…ó…óaŇčke on, mo∆ī∆īugol e maw…ďe makko …ďen. Si …ďe ndoolii maa fii cirkangol Kam, ko a alanaa …óum ganndal, wota a …óofto …ďe ! Ko ka Am, woni ruttorde mon, Mi habra on, ko ngollatno …óon."
  29,9,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe Alla, …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, ma Min mba…ótidu…ďe e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen."
  29,10,"Hino e jim…ďe …ďen, wi'oowo: ""Min ngooŇč…óinii Alla""; hara non si o tampiniraama fii Alla, o wa…óat lorra yim…ďe …ďen, wano lepte Alla …óen. Si ballal kadi immorii ka Joomi maa, pellet, …ďe mbi'ay: ""Mi…óen ngo'dunoo e mo'on!"" Kere wonaa Alla …ďuri anndu'de ko woni e …ďer…óe tageefo ngon?"
  29,11,"Ma Alla anndin fii gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, ma O fe√Ī√Īina kadi fii naafiqii…ďe …ďeen."
  29,12,"Heefer…ďe …ďen wi'ani gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen: ""Jokkee laawol amen ngol, men fawtoto fii goopi mon …óin"". Kono …ďe ngonaani fawtotoo…ďe hay hu'unde e goopi ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, ko …ďe fenoo…ďe."
  29,13,"Kono maa …ďe paawtoo fii teddeendi bakkaat ma…ď…ďe …óin, e teddeendi goo, wond'ude e teddeendi ma…ď…ďe ndin. Ko maa …ďe lamndoyee, √Ďande Darngal, ga e kon ko …ďe fekindotonoo."
  29,14,"GooŇč…óii Min nulii Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďen, o √Īii…ďi hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, duu…ďi ujunere, Ňčakku…óum duu…ďi cappan…óe jowi. Waame on nanngi …ďe, hari ko …ďe too√Ī…ďe."
  29,15,"Min nda…óndi mo, kaŇčko e yim…ďe laana kan; Min mba…ói ka kaawisa tageefo ngo."
  29,16,"(JaŇčto) kadi Ibraahiima, nde o wi'annoo yim…ďe makko …ďen: ""ndeewee Alla, kulon Mo; ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īann'de on, si woni ho…óon nganndi""."
  29,17,"Anndee ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko sanamuuji, ho…óon ta∆īa fenaande. Pellet, …óin …ói ndewoton ga Alla, …ói waawaa on arsikude; …óa…ď…ďiree arsike on ka Alla, rewon mo, ∆īetton Mo. Ko ka makko woni ruttete…óon."
  29,18,"Si on njeddi i, haray mofte adinoo…ďe kadi njeddiino (Nulaa…ďe mum). Alaa ko fawii e Nulaa…óo on, si wonaa yottingol …ďannginngol."
  29,19,"E …ďee yiaani no Alla fu…ó…óorta tagoore ngum, refti o ndttat ngu? Pellet, …óum wonii ko newanii Alla."
  29,20,"Maaku: ""Yiilee ka leydi, ndaaron no O pu…ó…óori tagoore. refti Alla tagoore sakkitoru ngum. Pellet, Alla ko kattan…óo kala hu'unde""."
  29,21,"Homo lepte mo o muuyani, o yurmo mo O muuyani; ko ka makko ruttete…óon."
  29,22,"On wonaani laawotoo…ďe ka leydi, wonaa ka kammu; alanaa on ga Alla, woni gi…óo, wanaa ballo."
  29,23,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe aayeeje Alla …óen, e hawroygol e makko ngol, …ďen ta∆īike e yurmeende Am, …ďen …óon, hono woodani …ďe lepte mu'usu…óe."
  29,24,"Jaabawol yim…ďe makko …ďen wonaano, si wonaa wiide …ďe: ""Waree mo, maa sunnon mo"". Kono Alla da…óndi mo e yiite ngen. Pellet, wonii e …óum, Ma'andeeji, wonan'de yim…ďe gooŇč…óim…ďe."
  29,25,"O maaki: ""nganndee ko ndewoton kon ga Alla, ko sanamuuji, fii yi…óindiro hakkunde mon, ka nguurndam aduna, hooti non, √Ďande Darndal, yoga mon yeddoyay yoga, yoga mon kadi hu…óo yoga, hara non, jaa∆īorde mon nden, ko ka Yiite, hara walloo…ďe alanaa on""."
  29,26,"Luutu gooŇč…óini mo. O maaki: ""Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, ko KaŇčko woni Foolu…óo, √Ďee√Īo On""."
  29,27,"Min nje…ói mo Ismaa'iila e Yaaquuba, Min mba…ói e ge√Īngol makko ngol, Annabaaku e Daftere. Min ngokki mo mbarjaari makko ndin aduna, pellet, kaŇčo on ka La'akara, ko o jeyaa…óo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen."
  29,28,"(JaŇčto) kadi luutu, nde o maakannoo yim…ďe makko …ďen : "" E on aray e paŇčkare, …óe gooto e winndere nden adaaki on e mun?"
  29,29,"E on aray jottagol e wor…ďe …ďen? palo…óon kadi e laawol? Ngollaton ko mbatirdu mon ko a√Īinii?"" Kono jaabawol yim…ďe makko …ďeen wonaano, si wonaa wiide …ďe: ""Addan men lepte Alla …óen, si tawii ko a jeyaa…óo e gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen""."
  29,30,"O maaki: ""Joomi am, wallam e hoore yim…ďe bonnoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  29,31,"Tuma nde Imminaa…ďe Amen …ďen addannoo Ibraahiima welo-welo ngon, …ďe mb""i: ""Minen, ko men halkoo…ďee yim…ďe ndee saare. Tawde pellet, yim…ďe mayre laatike too√Īoo…ďe""."
  29,32,"O maaki: ""Kono Luutu no ton!"" ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Ko minen …ďuri anndude fii won'…ďe ton. Ko ma men da…óndu mo, kaŇčko e yim…ďe makko …ďen, si wonaa debbo makko on, o jeyaama e helketee…ďe …ďeen""."
  29,33,"Tum nde imminaa…ďe Amen …ďen keewtunoo ka Luutu, o sa…ótiraa fii ma…ď…ďe, …ďernde makko …ďi…ótorii fii ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Wota a hul, wota a suno. Ko men da…óndoo…ďe ma an e …ďeynguure maa nde, si wonaa debbo maa on, o jeyaama e halkaa…ďe …ďen."
  29,34,"Ko moen njippinoo…ďe lepte e yim…ďe ndee saare, immorde ka kammu, sabu ko …ďe yaltunoo e …óoftaare kon""."
  29,35,"GooŇč…óii Min ngaccii e nden (saare), Ma'ande …ďanngunde, wonan'de yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe …ďeen."
  29,36,"(Min nuli) kadi e Madyana, musi…ó…óo ma…ď…ďe on, Shu'aybu. O maaki: ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla, jortoron √Ďalannde sakkitiinde nden, wota woniri e leydi ndin, bonnoo…ďe""."
  29,37,"Kono …ďe njeddi i mo. Dillannde nden nanngi …ďe, …ďe wa…ótini ka ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďe jiccii…ďe-maayi."
  29,38,"(Meon kalki) kadi Aadi'en, e Saamuda'en. GooŇč…óii caambbeje ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďannganii on. Seytaane cu…óinani …ďe, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen, ndu sakkii …ďe e laawol ngol; tawi le, ko …ďe reentunoo…ďe."
  29,39,"(Min kalki) kadi Qaaruuna, e Fir'awna e Haamaana. GooŇč…óii le, Muusaa addanii …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji, kono …ďe toownitii ka leydi, …ďe wonaano laawotoo…ďe."
  29,40,"Kala ma…ď…ďe, Min leptirno bakkaatuuji mum …óin: no e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Min ngurti henndu e mum; no e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe haacaango kalki; no e ma…ď…ďe, mo Min mutini …óum ka leydi, no e ma…ď…ďe kadi, …ďe Min yoolunoo. Kono non, Alla siforaali too√Īoowo …ďe; si ko woni, ko kam…ďe too√Īuoo ko'e ma…ď…ďe."
  29,41,"Misal …ďen jogitii…ďe ga Alla dewetee…ói, ko wano marijaawowal(njomblo) saccungal suudu. Ko …ďuri lo'ode non e cuu…ói …óin, ko suudu marijaawo. Sinno …ďe annduno!"
  29,42,"Pellet, Alla no anndi kala hu'unde nde …ďe noddata ga makko. Ko KaŇčko woni Fool…óo, √Ďee√Īo On."
  29,43,"∆äii ko yeruuji …óe Min piyanta yim…ďe …ďen; ko woni tun, paamataa …óen, si wonaa anndu…ďe …ďen."
  29,44,"Alla tagirii kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e hoore goonga. Pellet, wonii …óum, Ma'ande, wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  29,45,"Janngu …óum ko waayinaa e maa…óa ka deftere, √Īii…ďaa e juulde nden. Pellet, juulde nden no ha…óa paŇčkare e ko a√Īinii. Ko jantagol Alla ngol …ďuri (hu'unde kala) mawnude. Alla no anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  29,46,"Wota on wee√Īir yim…ďe defte …ďen si wonaa e no …ďuri e mo∆ī∆īirde, si wonaa hara ko …ďen too√Ī…ďe e ma…ď…ďe. Mbi'on: ""Min ngooŇč…óinii nden njippinaande e amen e …óen njippinaa…óe e mon. Dewetee…óo amen On e dewetee…óo mon On ko gooto, menen non, ko Min jebbilanii …ďe Mo""."
  29,47,"Ko wano non Min njippiniri e maa…óa Deftere nden. ∆Āeen …ďe Min ngokki Deftere nden, he…ďe mgooŇč…óini nde. Hino e ma…ď…ďe on gooŇč…óin…óo nde. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wonaa heefer…ďe …ďen."
  29,48,"A wonaano ha…óa janngatnoo deftere ado mayre, a winndirtaano √Īaamo maa ngon. Harayno, bonnoo…ďe …ďen cikkittono."
  29,49,"Si ko woni, ko nde Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe e …ďer…óe …ďen okkaa…ďe ganndal. Yeddataa aayeeje Amen …óen, si wonaa too√Ī…ďe …ďeen."
  29,50,"∆Āe mb'i: ""Hanno jippinee e makko Ma'andeeji immorde ka Joomi makko?"" Maaku: ""aayaaji ko joomam addata, anndee min, ko mi jeertinoowo …ďanngu…óo""."
  29,51,"Kere yonaani …ďe won'de Min njippinii e maa…óa deftere nden hende janngee e ma…ď…ďe? Wonii e …óuum, yurmeende e waaju wonan'de yim…ďe gooŇč…óinoo…ďe."
  29,52,"Maaku: ""Alla yonii hakkunde am e moo…óon seedee Hino anndi ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi. ∆Āen non gooŇč…óim…ďe meere nden …ďe yeddi Alla, ko …ďen ngoni oni sooy…ďe …ďen."
  29,53,"He…ďe kawjirane lepte …óen. Si wonaano fii lajal innaangal, lepte …óen ngardiratno e ma…ď…ďe juhal, hara kam…ďe …ďe so'aa-anndude."
  29,54,"He…ďe lawjirane lepte …óen, hara non pellet, Jahannama ko fiiltiinge heefere…ďe …ďeen."
  29,55,"√Ďande lepte …óen suddiroyta …ďe senngo dow ma…ď…ďe e ka ley koy…óe ma…ď…ďe, O daala[na …ďe]: ""Mee…óee ko ngollatno…óon kon!"""
  29,56,"Eey mon jiyaa…ďe Am goo…óin…ďe! Nganndee leydi Am ndin ko yaajundi. Ko Min ngoni ko ndewoton!"
  29,57,"Kala woŇčkii mee…óay maayde. refti ko ka Amen nduttete…óon."
  29,58,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, ma Min ko…ónu …ďe ka Aljanna e cuu…ói …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley majji, ko…ďe duumotoo…ďe ton. Iskin(heskey)¬į mo∆ī∆īere njo…ďdi gollunoo…ďe,"
  29,59,"…ďeen mu√Ī√Īii…ďe, …ďe tuugii e Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  29,60,"Heewii e ruugat…ói …ói yoo…ďotaako arsike majji! Ko Alla arsikata …ói wond'ude e onon. Ko KaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ganndu…óo."
  29,61,"Pellet, si a la…ďndiima …ďe: ""Ko hommbo tagi kammuu- li …óiin e leydi ndin, O elti na'ange nge e lewru ndu?"" Ma …ďe mbi'u: ""Ko Alla"". Ko holno …ďe ferlitoraa (e gooŇč…óingol ngol)?"
  29,62,"Alla no yaacnana arsike on mo o muuyi e jiyaa…ďe makko …ďen, Homo …ďittana mo. Pellet, Alla ko ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
  29,63,"Pellet, si a lanndike …ďe: ""Ko hommbo jippiniri ndiyam ka kammu …óam O wuurnitiri leydi ndin …ďaawo ndi yoorde?"", ma …ďe mbi': ""Ko Alla"". Maaku: ""Yettoore woodanii Alla!"". Si ko woni, ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe kaqqiltaa."
  29,64,"∆äam nguurndam aduna wonaani, si wonaa mbelee…óe e fijindaaru. Pellet, ko ho…óo La'akara ngon woni nguurandam. Sinno …ďe annduno."
  29,65,"Si …ďe wa…ó…óike ka laana, …ďe nodda Alla …ďe la…ď…ďinano mo noddaandu ndun. Tuma nde o da…óndi …ďe ka njoorndi, on tuma …ďe cirka."
  29,66,"No …ďe yeddira ko Min ngokki …ďe kon, awa yo …ďe dakmito! Aray ka…ďe ngannda."
  29,67,"E …ďee nji'aani won'de Min mba…óii hormorde hoolniinde, yim…ďe …ďen no ci'ifee(mbifte) bannge ma…ď…ďe? E ko meere nden …ďe ngooŇč…óinta …ďe njedda neemaaji Alla …óin?"
  29,68,"E ko hommbo …ďuri too√Īide wa on pekondii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o fenni goonga kan nde ka arnoo e makko? E wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆īorde yeddu…ďe …ďen?"
  29,69,"∆Āeen tii…ónor…ďe e (weltingol) Min, ma Min peewnir…ďe e laawi Amen, ko pellet, Alla no won'di e mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďeen."
